definitions.definition: A man who travels around with a swag ( “ bundle of personal items ” ) ; specifically, an itinerant person, often seeking work in exchange for food and lodging .
A person who sells or trades in trinkets or items of low value .
A middleman who buys and sells stolen goods ; a fence .

main_definition: ( Australia , New Zealand , historical ) A man who travels around with a swag ( “ bundle of personal items ” ) ; specifically, an itinerant person, often seeking work in exchange for food and lodging .
secondary_definitions: ( British , archaic ) A person who sells or trades in trinkets or items of low value .
( US , slang ) A middleman who buys and sells stolen goods ; a fence .
